  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ITA27">
<l>patiyamaintu nāṭip parutteḻunta cintai</l>
<l>matiyuriñci vāṉmukaṭu nōkkik – katimikuttaṅ</l>
<l>kōṟēṭi yōṭuṅ koḻuntatē pōṉṟatē</l>
<l>māṟēṭi yōṭu maṉam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mind  that settles in a place [but] rises, searching, growing,</l>
<l>resembles a shoot that looks up to the sky, rubbing against the moon,</l>
<l>with increasing speed, running in search of a good support,</l>
<l>– the mind that runs in search of Māl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
